OL,7,FA charity originally formed to unite
OL,8,Fmen through walking and talking is now
OL,9,Fproviding mental health support to
OL,10,Fsteelworkers in Port Talbot.JTata
OL,11,FSteel announced last Friday (19
OL,12,FDecember) plans to cut 2,500 jobs at
OL,13,Fthe plant as it moves towards a
OL,14,Fgreener way of making steel.
OL,16,FA company spokesperson told ITV Wales
OL,17,Fit will start the "formal information
OL,18,Fsharing" and "consultation process
OL,19,Fshortly".
