OL,7,FThe uncertainty is having an impact on
OL,8,Fpeople's wellbeing. Marauders Men's
OL,9,FHealth team project manager Adam
OL,10,FDowney said: "A lot of people are
OL,11,Fworrying and they don't know if they
OL,12,Fare going to have their jobs next year.
OL,14,F"Like most people, they've got their
OL,15,Fcredit card debt, they've got their
OL,16,Fmortgages, they've got their car
OL,17,Ffinance and because they are not sure
OL,18,Fwhat's going to happen.
