OL,7,FHe added: "We help men in various
OL,8,Fways, we've got our well-being
OL,9,Ffootball, we have got our walks,
OL,10,Fcoffee mornings, we have our social
OL,11,Fevents, it's a community really,
OL,12,Fwhether you are one part of south
OL,13,FWales or another part of south Wales.
OL,15,F"We're all in it together and we're
OL,16,Fhelping each other and it's growing
OL,17,Fday by day."
