OL,7,F"We explain to them that it's about
OL,8,Fbreaking the stigma. Then we tell them
OL,9,Fwhat choices they have and it's always
OL,10,Fabout community and what we can give
OL,11,Fback to them."
OL,13,FTata Steel says it "understands" how
OL,14,Fdifficult the recent announcement has
OL,15,Fbeen for its workers and the steel
OL,16,Fcommunities.
OL,18,FA spokesperson told ITV Wales that it
OL,19,F"has an extensive network of support
OL,20,Fsystems available to employees".
