OL,7,FThey added: "Not only do we have our
OL,8,Fown line managers, HR professionals,
OL,9,Ftrades union representatives and
OL,10,FOccupational Health department with
OL,11,Fmental health specialists, employees
OL,12,Falso have access to a free,
OL,13,Findependently-managed, 24/7 Employee
OL,14,FAssistance Programme.
OL,16,F"More recently, together with our
OL,17,Ftrade union colleagues, we have
OL,18,Fsupported the training and development
OL,19,Fof nearly 400 mental health first
OL,20,Faiders across the business".
